[09/07/2019 09:00:31] <font color="#ffffff">(Música)</font>
[09/07/2019 09:00:34] <font color="#ffff00">"La guitarrista y blues woman</font>
[09/07/2019 09:00:34] <font color="#ffff00">Susan Santos</font>
[09/07/2019 09:00:36] <font color="#ffff00">publica</font>
[09/07/2019 09:00:36] <font color="#ffff00">su quinto álbum discográfico:</font>
[09/07/2019 09:00:39] <font color="#ffff00">'No U turn',</font>
[09/07/2019 09:00:39] <font color="#ffff00">prohibido cambiar de sentido.</font>
